        "details": "<div class=\"value-sans\">\n<p class=\"blue-text value-medium\">Fed up with the amount of plastic bottles they had to carry around their home, they decided to do something about it \n\n</p>\n<span class=\"gray-text\">They both knew the power and joy in natural cleaning, so they started experimenting with formulas in their garage. It's there that they conjured up Counter Clean for all around the home, and Bathroom Bliss for tricky water stains.\n</span>\n</div>"
      }
